Module JHigh2Low


module JHigh2Low: sig .. end
Tranformation of high level classes to low level classes.
val high2low : JCode.jcode JClass.interface_or_class -> JClassLow.jclass
Convert a high level class to a lower level class.

h2l_* functions are used in the JDump module so functions of JDumpLow can be used.
val h2l_cfield : JBasics.constant DynArray.t -> JClass.class_field -> JClassLow.jfield
val h2l_ifield : JBasics.constant DynArray.t -> JClass.interface_field -> JClassLow.jfield
val h2l_cmethod : JBasics.constant DynArray.t ->
       JCode.jcode JClass.concrete_method -> JClassLow.jmethod
val h2l_amethod : JBasics.constant DynArray.t -> JClass.abstract_method -> JClassLow.jmethod
val h2l_acmethod : JBasics.constant DynArray.t ->
       JCode.jcode JClass.jmethod -> JClassLow.jmethod
